data.text:
Identify Equivalent Fractions

Answer each question.

1. Which fractions are equivalent to  1 4 ? Choose all that apply.

     

    4 7 ,
    3 12 ,
    10 40 ,
    11 14 ,
    7 28 ,
    9 32
     
  2. Which fractions are equivalent to  6 9 ? Choose all that apply.

     

    2 3 ,
    4 6 ,
    5 8 ,
    7 10 ,
    24 36 ,
    16 19
